    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team accepted the package on the basis that achieved levels, while below required levels in several factors, are sufficient for the intended regulatory submission context given the conservative Monte Carlo uncertainty bounds. The team noted that the rheology dataset (dataVintage 2025-10-01) predates the model revision (2026-01-15) and that re-validation of model input parameters is planned for Q2 2026. No formal gap closure was required prior to acceptance. Six factors remain not-assessed as documented epistemic gaps.",
